        <abstract>
            <p>Longs to be on the other side of the Horn; tired of these countries. Natural history makes him continue. He now knows it will remain his favourite pursuit for the rest of his life.</p>
            <p>Comments on slavery.</p>
            <p>Will have additional space on board and a servant [Syms Covington] who will help him with the collection of birds and quadrupeds.</p>
            <p>Asks for books, a lens, and four pairs of shoes.</p>
        </abstract>
